                                    <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 com-xs-12">\r\n                                               <div class="img-block">\r\n                                                   <img data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" data-title="Feedback" src="https://bltscottsdale.com/wp-content/themes/pashmina/images/blank.png" alt="Hyunot">\r\n                                               </div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n                                       </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div><div class="template-1">\r\n                                    <div class="container">\r\n                                       <div class="item">\r\n                                          <div class="row">\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 com-xs-12" contenteditable="false">\r\n                                                <h2>Tnjre<br></h2>\r\n                                                <p>The “Tnjre” international classical music festival of young performers gathers famous and young musicians from Karabakh and all over the world in June.  During the festival famous musicians from Germany, Italy, Finland, Netherlands and other countries organize master classes of piano, violin and clarinet for the inhabitants and guests of Artsakh. Concerts are held in the capital city and regional centers during the festival. </p>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 com-xs-12">\r\n                                               <div class="img-block">\r\n                                                   <img data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" data-title="Feedback" src="https://bltscottsdale.com/wp-content/themes/pashmina/images/blank.png" alt="Hyunot">\r\n                                               </div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n                                       </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div><div class="template-1">\r\n                                    <div class="container">\r\n                                       <div class="item">\r\n                                          <div class="row">\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 com-xs-12" contenteditable="false">\r\n                                                <h2>Harvest fair<br></h2>\r\n                                                <p>Harvest fair. The second Sunday of October is celebrated as the Day of Agriculture. Every year a Harvest Festival is organized this day  in the Stepanakert Renaissance Square.  More than 200 vendors from all the regions of Artsakh introduce their production to the thousands of visitors that attended the fair.  </p>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 com-xs-12">\r\n                                               <div class="img-block">\r\n                                                   <img data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" data-title="Feedback" src="https://bltscottsdale.com/wp-content/themes/pashmina/images/blank.png" alt="Hyunot">\r\n                                               </div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n                                       </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div><div class="template-1">\r\n                                    <div class="container">\r\n                                       <div class="item">\r\n                                          <div class="row">\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 com-xs-12" contenteditable="false">\r\n                                                <h2>Artsakh Wine Festival</h2>\r\n                                                <p>Artsakh Wine Festival is celebrated on the third Saturday of October and symbolizes the end of harvesting of grape. The fest is organized in the spirit of pastime, entertainment and rest. Festival guests are treated with famous Artsakh wine and delicious Artsakh cuisine. A harvest fair-exhibition, folk music concert, traditional games, handmade works exhibition are organized during the fest. </p>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 com-xs-12">\r\n                                               <div class="img-block">\r\n                                                   <img data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" data-title="Feedback" src="https://bltscottsdale.com/wp-content/themes/pashmina/images/blank.png" alt="Hyunot">\r\n                                               </div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n                                       </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div><div class="template-1">\r\n                                    <div class="container">\r\n                                       <div class="item">\r\n                                          <div class="row">\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 com-xs-12" contenteditable="false">\r\n                                                <h2>Religious holidays<br></h2>\r\n                                                <p>Religious holidays - Christmas and Christmas Eve – are celebrated with great enthusiasm. On these days are organized folk festivals, various religious and cultural events. </p>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 com-xs-12">\r\n                                               <div class="img-block">\r\n                                                   <img data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" data-title="Feedback" src="https://bltscottsdale.com/wp-content/themes/pashmina/images/blank.png" alt="Hyunot">\r\n                                               </div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n                                       </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 7, 'http://storage.loc/source', '1/T1Nb3ZeTxBl-HM0sGvwcEcuxKddng11S.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1519512911, 1519512911, 1520664574);
